workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
You've developed great strength and size in your shoulders, now let's take it over the top.


You'll be doing a high volume of reps, so nail your form on the new moves with the tutorial, and don't let your standards slip.

groups.title: Warm-up
groups.summary: Get your muscles firing and shoulder joints moving smoothly.
